OL,3,CRemembering Nimroy on what would have
OL,4,Cbeen his 30th birthday
OL,6,FThe father of a man who died after
OL,7,Fbeing stabbed in Sussex has released a
OL,8,Fsong to mark what would have been his
OL,9,Fson's 30th birthday.
OL,11,FNimroy Hendricks Senior has been
OL,12,Fcampaigning to prevent knife crime
OL,13,Fever since Nimroy Junior was killed.
OL,15,FThe 24-year-old was stabbed in the
OL,16,Fchest by a 14-year-old girl in the
OL,17,FThree Bridges area of Crawley on
OL,18,FOctober 27, 2020.
