OL,3,CRemembering Nimroy on what would have
OL,4,Cbeen his 30th birthday
OL,6,FThe teenager, who can't be named for
OL,7,Flegal reasons, pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fmanslaughter on the grounds of
OL,9,Fdiminished responsibility and was
OL,10,Fjailed for five years, to serve
OL,11,Fanother four years on licence.
OL,13,FIn September 2025, a coroner found
OL,14,Fpotentially missed opportunities to
OL,15,Fprevent her committing violence and
OL,16,Fauthorities have acknowledged the
OL,17,Ffindings.
