OL,3,CRemembering Nimroy on what would have
OL,4,Cbeen his 30th birthday
OL,6,FBonded by a shared love of music,
OL,7,FNimroy Senior is honouring his son's
OL,8,Fpassion by releasing a heartfelt track
OL,9,Fcalled 'Life is not the same without
OL,10,Fyou'.
OL,12,FNimroy Junior's voice features
OL,13,Fthroughout, which is aimed at striking
OL,14,Fa sobering chord.
OL,16,FNimroy Senior said: "The death of Nim
OL,17,Fhas made us all a broken family
OL,18,Fbecause of the person that Nim was so
OL,19,Fit's really, really deep for us in
OL,20,Fterms of what really happened here.
