OL,3,CRemembering Nimroy on what would have
OL,4,Cbeen his 30th birthday
OL,6,F"There's no way we can get over it and
OL,7,Flots of times we struggle from one day
OL,8,Fto another."
OL,10,FNimroy Senior told ITV News Meridian
OL,11,Fhe wants the loss of his son to
OL,12,Fhighlight the devastating impact of
OL,13,Fknife crime.
OL,15,FHe said: "It's because of Nim why we
OL,16,Fdid this song.
OL,18,F"As an artist, when I look and see the
OL,19,Fother parents who are suffering this
OL,20,Floss because of knives, it does grieve
OL,21,Fme."
